content.query:
SELECT TOP (100) [VendorID]
,[lpep_pickup_datetime]
,[lpep_dropoff_datetime]
,[store_and_fwd_flag]
,[RatecodeID]
,[PULocationID]
,[DOLocationID]
,[passenger_count]
,[trip_distance]
,[fare_amount]
,[extra]
,[mta_tax]
,[tip_amount]
,[tolls_amount]
,[ehail_fee]
,[improvement_surcharge]
,[total_amount]
,[payment_type]
,[trip_type]
,[congestion_surcharge]
 FROM [bronze].[trip_data_green_csv]
 where [ehail_fee] is not null
